{"tid":1304940,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭重向啱啱係油塘大本型外面影相既一位嬸嬸道歉","createTime":"2019-07-10T17:41:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T19:42:29.000Z","uid":4026,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7c312262e34ffb1d68bb6a196b77aaa433b1e328","tid":1304940,"uid":4026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:41:30.000Z","msg":"啱啱發夢係油塘同班巴打一齊圍住班狗<br />\n但突然聽到有個手足罵個呀嬸影完未<br />\n然後我同成班手足就一齊圍住個呀嬸唔比佢走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知個呀嬸同我地講 佢係反送中 反黑警 <br />\n佢只係想影班黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但基於佢有少少口音同年紀都偏老<br />\n果下我地都好先入為主咁覺得佢係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以就叫人讓開條路 比個呀嬸企最前影<br />\n但可能一黎佢本身冇帶口罩 二黎成班手足開始起哄<br />\n就嚇到佢唔知點算好 想走又比人攔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直到有人企出黎同個呀嬸做證<br />\n證明佢好早就到現場一齊罵班藍絲<br />\n重好大聲一齊嗌：「無線新聞，事事旦旦，香港警察，知法犯法」<br />\n大家先知原來誤會左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然知道果位嬸嬸冇咩可能會上連登<br />\n但都希望同佢再講返聲對唔住<br />\n同埋想係到還佢一個清白<br />\n因為現場當時應該好多人都唔知咩事<br />\n<br />\n對唔住呀！！！！！嬸嬸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b8d1014bb7135753206a36eb09432c31761ea1","tid":1304940,"uid":76058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:42:00.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"378867301e6f778dbcce8126ef3cc2f3f0b7182f","tid":1304940,"uid":4026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:42:45.000Z","msg":"推！！！！"},{"pid":"e65ae398671dde06393dfd522470c72dcc77eac5","tid":1304940,"uid":116821,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:42:53.000Z","msg":"都好難怪大家<br />\n頭先落到去都要過一陣先知企錯邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝婆婆身體健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc8b41c051b9679f9790eeea22ce50d0fc452f04","tid":1304940,"uid":34047,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:42:57.000Z","msg":"有時現場人有人舉機 大家都會反應大 因為真係怕同路人被影 不過又真係要諗下點避免鬧錯同路人"},{"pid":"335ff42eacac6bde4f74aecdad82fc56e41b49b6","tid":1304940,"uid":4026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:43:49.000Z","msg":"但無論邊個都好<br />\n下次真係唔好再係現場影相　特別係大頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26b72b5da3e4bec44d767a3c8659488f22509031","tid":1304940,"uid":4026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e65ae398671dde06393dfd522470c72dcc77eac5","tid":1304940,"uid":116821,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:42:53.000Z","msg":"都好難怪大家<br />\n頭先落到去都要過一陣先知企錯邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝婆婆身體健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:44:37.000Z","msg":"我果下都有份攔住佢唔比佢走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d408a282ccb4244042e515230e82eaf07be359f0","tid":1304940,"uid":213946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26b72b5da3e4bec44d767a3c8659488f22509031","tid":1304940,"uid":4026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e65ae398671dde06393dfd522470c72dcc77eac5","tid":1304940,"uid":116821,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:42:53.000Z","msg":"都好難怪大家<br />\n頭先落到去都要過一陣先知企錯邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝婆婆身體健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:44:37.000Z","msg":"我果下都有份攔住佢唔比佢走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:45:05.000Z","msg":"佢會諒解嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e268a5a64d0008527b652f7589